replies.bodyText:
In fact, should this entire method be just
private static boolean isZero(Number number) {
    return number.longValue() == 0L; // || number.doubleValue() == 0.0;
}
That would also cover numeric values from other libraries, such as Guava or Apache Commons Lang.

